A Half-Life Storm Studios Collaboration

's request for a 1.6 to source map remake of a map he originally designed and had created by another mapper. See the original Map here:
aim_hts_aztec Embedded into the bsp: Custom Radar Overview/Code designed by Rokusho Hand Built Custom Nav File designed by Lost ->Radar Place Names Included Full Ambient Soundscape designed by Rokusho The Download file contains the bzip'd version of the map for server administrators to quickly add into their fast-downloads server, to open the bzip'd file you will require winrar to get to the normal bsp file.
